#| "the transactions in which it appears."
msgid ""
"To rename a payee or payer, select the payee (left click the name) and click "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"user-group-"
"properties.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
